# Core Product Pitch Deck – Doctrine & Build Guide

Purpose: Provide a slide-by-slide outline for a core product pitch deck, with the exact messages, proof points, visuals, and live-demo hooks. Another agent should be able to assemble the deck and run the live demo using this rule.

RUO posture: Research-use only. No clinical claims. Provenance and disclaimers must be visible.

## Audience and Goal
- Audience: Investors, strategic partners, biotech R&D leaders
- Goal: Show a credible, demo-complete in‑silico therapeutic design and validation platform with clear value, traction path, and moats.

## Narrative Arc (30–35 min)
1) The Problem → 2) The Solution → 3) How It Works → 4) Live Demo → 5) Evidence & Metrics → 6) Business & Moats → 7) Roadmap & Ask

