## Demo Runbook (1‑pager)
- Backend: `uvicorn api.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000` (ensure `api/main.py` indentation fixed)
- Env flags: `EVO_FORCE_MODEL=evo2_1b`, `EVO_USE_DELTA_ONLY=1`, `DISABLE_LITERATURE=1`, optional `DISABLE_FUSION=1`
- Redis (optional): `docker run -p 6379:6379 redis:7`
- Sanity checks:
  - `GET /openapi.json` → 200
  - `POST /api/efficacy/predict` (BRAF V600E example) → ranked drugs returned
  - `POST /api/insights/predict_gene_essentiality` → score ∈ [0,1], `provenance` present
  - `POST /api/datasets/extract_and_benchmark` → metrics JSON

## Endpoint Map (Deck → Live)
- WIWFM: `POST /api/efficacy/predict`
- Insights: `POST /api/insights/predict_*`
- Fusion coverage (AM): `GET /api/fusion/coverage`
